1. PRE-REQUISITES
=================

For Linux version :
    - GCC compiler (gcc) and make tools
    - Gtk+ 2.0 libraries & headers
    - Libxml2 (provided with Gnome)

For Windows version :
    - Mingw compiler, installed in C:\mingw (http://www.mingw.org)
    - Gtk+ 2.0 libraries & headers (http://www.gimp.org/~tml/gimp/win32)
    - Libxml2 (http://www.libxml.org)


2. COMPILATION
==============

Linux/GTK :

    ./configure
    make

Linux/Gnome :

    cd src
    make -f Makefile.gnome

Windows :
    cd src
    m.bat


3. INSTALLATION
===============

make install

Create .gmemo directory in your home :

mkdir ~/.gmemo

Copy feasts & memos :

cp gmemo_feasts.xml ~/.gmemo/
cp gmemo.xml ~/.gmemo/


4. RUNNING GMEMO
================

Getting help under Linux :
./gmemo --help

Getting help under Win32 :
not yet developed


